                .page-footer__copyright
                  | &copy; Copyright 2021 Greece.ru
                  p Real estate agency with the&nbsp;best properties. Become a&nbsp;part of&nbsp;our&nbsp;community.
                p.page-footer__address
                  | Greece, Thessaloniki, Nikis Ave 1,  floor 2, 56424,
                  a(href='tel:+306974383') +30 6974-383
              ul.page-footer__list
